mparisons between the two taxa. We highlight the need for multiple lines of evidence to solve the remaining taxonomic problems among the remaining species complexes in Lophostoma.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Esquivel, Diego A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Pereira, Maria Jo\u00e1o Ramos", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Stuhler, John D.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Rossoni, Daniela M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Velazco, Pa\u00fal M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Bianchi, Filipe Michels", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/dfca4ff684c3d47012e5e0376f5fc3d8", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/ce1212343760d5a450d1d2c4165d2d5c09e4d45968cc77667dc1578ae5a4f0db", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/SLR9XWK4", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/SLR9XWK4", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/e455742d25803918538230a1fd68e45b!/b78659-81129", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "1", "pages": "1-21", "title": "Systematics and Biodiversity", "volume": "20"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/dfca4ff684c3d47012e5e0376f5fc3d8"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:SLR9XWK4"}, {"i